A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Code Section 12-2-2 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to
2 Environmental Protection Division, Environmental Advisory Council, duties of council and
3 its members and director, appeal procedures generally, permit applications, and inspections,
4 so as to update the reference date to standards, rules, and regulations; to amend Title 27 of
5 the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to game and fish, so as to update the
6 reference date to rules and regulations; to provide for courtesy hunting and fishing licenses
7 for paralyzed or disabled individuals; to change an age requirement for the special turkey
8 hunting season for young and mobility impaired hunters; to provide for fees for resident
9 shellfish crews; to amend Code Section 52-7-26 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated,
10 relating to penalty, so as to update the reference date to rules and regulations; to provide for
11 related matters; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
13 SECTION 1.
